Onnanoko ni Naritai:
Music video for the song Onnanoko ni Naritai by Japanese utaite singer Mafumafu that was featured on his fifth full-length album "Kagura Iro Artifact". The music video was animated by MONO-Devoid.

A boy doesn't want to be one anymore and instead would much prefer to a cute girl and live out the fantasy of Cinderella.
